    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and transmission slips, alongside notable body damage such as deep rust patches and large dents. The interior has sustained heavy wear with multiple tears in the seating and several broken plastic trim pieces, making it a candidate for a full restoration or a parts donor.",
